<h1>SDL-Bullethell</h1>
<p>Project repo: <a href='https://github.com/nathan242/sdl-bullethell'>LINK</a></p>
<p>Compiled to WebAssembly: <a href='apps/bullethell/bullethell.html'>PLAY IN BROWSER</a></p>

<h4>Introduction</h4>
<p>Bullethell space shooter game in C++ using SDL2.</p>
<p>This is a work in progress. Once you reach the last set of enemies the game will loop round to the first set.</p>
<img src='images/bullethell_1.png' style='border: 1px solid; border-color; #000000;' width='500' height='391'>
<img src='images/bullethell_2.png' style='border: 1px solid; border-color; #000000;' width='500' height='391'>

<h4>Details</h4>
<p>Use the arrow keys to move the spaceship. Hold space to fire and press right shift to enable the shield once it is fully charged.</p>

